comment: Global offset is 0.5 (compensating indentation of gen2/3 printhead during homing). Vol. T1: 500 µL. First 9/10 layers disabled -> printing of ca. 1 mm layer in one step. All discs complete and well-defined. Collection in tube with DPBS until digestion assay.
